{"tid":454651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又超越香港】深圳屋苑違規施工　鑿穿地鐵隧道湧泥水","createTime":"2017-11-01T10:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T00:50:03.000Z","uid":43189,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bcef44ec3dd33f53088f5d06ea8b493121f62351","tid":454651,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T10:51:43.000Z","msg":"深圳一個屋苑早前違規施工期間，意外鑿穿地鐵隧道，令大量泥水流入。除泥水外，更有直徑達7厘米（約2&frac34;吋）、重約1公斤（約2磅）的石屎芯由鑿穿的缺口中墮入隧道。<br />\n<br />\n事發於本週六（28日），當時隧道內有列車正在行駛，幸而隧道遭鑿穿後，工作人員及早發現並聯絡相關部門搶修，事件中未有人受傷。工作人員其後在現場清走120袋泥，隧道中有多條電纜變形，現場亦有大量泥漬。<br />\n<br />\n深圳地鐵表示，屋苑進行工程前未有獲批，地鐵現時用鋼板等物料塞住缺口，其後將會用石屎補回。昨日（29日）至11月5日行車期間，亦會安排地鐵職員跟車檢查，以及限速至時速45公里以保安全。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.post852.com/233635/%e3%80%90%e5%a4%a7%e5%9c%8b%e3%80%8c%e7%98%8b%e3%80%8d%e7%af%84%e3%80%91%e6%b7%b1%e5%9c%b3%e5%b1%8b%e8%8b%91%e9%81%95%e8%a6%8f%e6%96%bd%e5%b7%a5%e3%80%80%e9%91%bf%e7%a9%bf%e5%9c%b0%e9%90%b5%e9%9a%a7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F233635%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%259c%258b%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%2598%258b%25e3%2580%258d%25e7%25af%2584%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%25b7%25b1%25e5%259c%25b3%25e5%25b1%258b%25e8%258b%2591%25e9%2581%2595%25e8%25a6%258f%25e6%2596%25bd%25e5%25b7%25a5%25e3%2580%2580%25e9%2591%25bf%25e7%25a9%25bf%25e5%259c%25b0%25e9%2590%25b5%25e9%259a%25a7%2F&d=5Ig7k8CSy%2Bo7Wa2EojChWv7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=bfa5751b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.post852.com/233635/%e3%80%90%e5%a4%a7%e5%9c%8b%e3%80%8c%e7%98%8b%e3%80%8d%e7%af%84%e3%80%91%e6%b7%b1%e5%9c%b3%e5%b1%8b%e8%8b%91%e9%81%95%e8%a6%8f%e6%96%bd%e5%b7%a5%e3%80%80%e9%91%bf%e7%a9%bf%e5%9c%b0%e9%90%b5%e9%9a%a7/</a>"},{"pid":"3f26ef004547672d03924689809b4614d8df5921","tid":454651,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T11:04:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"016d4d87283f06fff17a30484dd84093c7fa221e","tid":454651,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":2,"s